libs.content:
find_library(odbc_library
	names unixodbc iodbc odbc odbc32
	hints
		${odbc_root_dir}/lib
		${odbc_root_library_dirs}
	paths
		${pc_odbc_library_dirs}
		/usr/lib
		/usr/local/lib
		/usr/local/odbc/lib
		/usr/local/iodbc/lib
		"c:/program files/odbc/lib"
		"c:/odbc/lib/debug"
		"c:/program files (x86)/microsoft sdks/windows/v7.0a/lib"
		"${kit81_dir}/lib/winv6.3/um"
		"${kit_dir}/lib/win8/um"
	path_sufixes
		odbc
		x86
	doc "specify the odbc driver manager library here."
)

find_library(_lib_path
		names ${_lib_name}
		hints
			${odbc_root_dir}/lib
			${odbc_root_library_dirs}
		paths
			${pc_odbc_library_dirs}
			/usr/lib
			/usr/local/lib
			/usr/local/odbc/lib
			/usr/local/iodbc/lib
			"c:/program files/odbc/lib"
			"c:/odbc/lib/debug"
			"c:/program files (x86)/microsoft sdks/windows/v7.0a/lib"
		path_suffixes
			odbc
	)

find_library(mysql_library names mysqlclient
				 hints
					${mysql_root_dir}/lib
					${mysql_root_library_dirs}
				 paths
					 ${pc_mysql_library_dirs}
					 ${pc_mariadb_library_dirs}
					 $env{mysql_dir}/lib
					 $env{mysql_dir}/libmysql
					 $env{mysql_dir}/client
					 $env{programfiles}/mysql/*/lib
					 ${bindir32}/mysql/*/lib
					 $env{systemdrive}/mysql/*/lib
				 path_suffixes
				 	vs12
				 	vs11
				 	vs10
				 	opt
				 	release
	)

find_library(mysql_library names mysqlclient mysqlclient_r mariadbclient
				 hints
					${mysql_root_dir}/lib
					${mysql_root_library_dirs}
				 paths
					 ${pc_mysql_library_dirs}
					 ${pc_mariadb_library_dirs}
					 /usr/lib
					 /usr/local/lib
					 /usr/local/mysql/lib
					 /opt/mysql/mysql/lib
					 $env{mysql_dir}/libmysql_r/.libs
					 $env{mysql_dir}/lib
					 ${mysql_dir}/lib
				 path_suffixes
					mysql
					mariadb
		)

find_program(cmake_mc_compiler mc.exe hints "${sdk_bindir}" "${kit_bindir}" "${kit81_bindir}" ${kit10_bindir}
		doc "path to message compiler")
find_library(sqlite3_library names sqlite3 sqlite)
find_library(expat_library names expat libexpat hints ${pc_expat_library_dirs})
